        <div class="body">
            <p>find() does not support the usage of Zend_Db_Table_Select objects, it is a decorative interface into the functionality of fetchAll().  If you want to use a select object, you're better off passing into fetchAll() as it will be more indicative and expressive of what you are attempting to do.</p>

